    "section_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/body-nested-models/#list-fields",
    "section_text": "You can define an attribute to be a subtype. For example, a Python list :\n\nThis will make tags be a list, although it doesn't declare the type of the elements of the list.",
